%% Lifecycle of an event in the Gateway's local store.
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> RECEIVED: validated + persisted
    RECEIVED --> APPLIED: Account Service 2xx
    RECEIVED --> QUEUED: timeout / 5xx / CB open
    RECEIVED --> FAILED: Account Service 4xx (permanent)
    QUEUED --> APPLIED: outbox replayer succeeds
    QUEUED --> FAILED: replay hits permanent 4xx
    APPLIED --> APPLIED: duplicate POST (idempotent hit)
    FAILED --> [*]
    APPLIED --> [*]
